        "subject": "LU-2775 fid: allow FID-on-OST in fid_seq_is_mdt()",
        "message": "LU-2775 fid: allow FID-on-OST in fid_seq_is_mdt()\n\nThe old 2.1 fid_seq_is_mdt() was only checking for FID_SEQ_OST_MDT0\nthrough FID_SEQ_OST_MDT9 values, but this immediately breaks with\nFID-on-OST when enabled on 2.4 MDTs/OSTs.  That will be fixed in\na separate 2.4 patch, but the client should not LASSERT() on a\nvalue that it got from the network.  This will also allow the\nclient to at least access files on MDT0, even if it cannot handle\nfiles on remote MDTs properly.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I74bc9198799045b8bd91510cb45e8f8765300c1e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
